{"type": "article", "id": 14964, "title": "露肩设计、竖条纹和低腰裤|每天都有流行关键词", "description": "我们每天为你总结秀场流行元素。", "date": "2015-09-16T08:41:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 16089, "name": "一字领"}, {"id": 10698, "name": "露肩"}, {"id": 16090, "name": "低腰裤"}, {"id": 16091, "name": "竖条纹"}, {"id": 7048, "name": "纽约时装周"}, {"id": 3322, "name": "Givenchy"}, {"id": 16092, "name": "TIBI"}, {"id": 2855, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021244527No395mUs0kVcnKe.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t时装周这种盛事总归有很多看头，秀场上的服装、鞋包、配饰等全套造型，下一季的流行趋势，前来看秀的人各展神功留下的有型街拍，后台的抓拍，前排的大佬……\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124447LUBtnTM4gF3c5Ppo.jpg\" width=\"980\" height=\"490\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t本月 9 日开幕的纽约时装周已经马不停蹄过去了快一个星期，不如就回归初心，看看已经出场的品牌们，哪些小的设计细节频繁出现？\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t露肩设计：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t从上一个春季流行的一字领，发展到今年更常见更大胆的露肩装，性感又清凉，还平添了足够 Cool 的元素。让姑娘露出优美肩线更具吸引力的同时，原本基础款的上衣也变得别致起来。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124447i4ZDV1gH2KoteQ3J.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Adeam </em><span style=\"text-align:center;\">△</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124448vCh7sGkNtJl92oxz.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Giulietta </em><span style=\"text-align:center;\">△</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124448b84vwpOdlrDIhfZk.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>TIBI </em><span style=\"text-align:center;\">△</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212444963zA5g9RMyeSTlEi.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>15 日刚结束的 Tory Burch</em><span style=\"text-align:center;\">  △</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t彩色竖条纹：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t运用竖条纹特别多的，除了条形码，还有这季的 Alexander Wang——风衣、夹克、长裙、裤子无一例外。除了拉长视觉效果，还穿出了王大仁一贯的中性风。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124449VCF7s0kIaD2B9NcK.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124450b8RU0fkudL1YXgEx.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em>Alexander Wang </em><span style=\"text-align:center;\">△</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124450BVafylukPnJKYjRh.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Tory Burch</em>  △\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124450undG3B7vMDbCIkEw.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Tanya Taylor</em> △\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124451VzSFN4RLW6fED0An.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Tse </em><span style=\"text-align:center;\">△</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t低腰裤：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这种休闲的、松松垮垮的风格，比阔腿裤还要随性（只是可能没阔腿裤有型），90 年代流行于摇滚歌手、街舞小子之中，如今以更时髦的方式重归秀场。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124451SgvqNFkdDYGWb3OJ.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em> Tommy Hilfiger</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124452xaLcOwqe62kQ50ig.jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"647\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Derek lam / Victor Alfaro</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<i></i><em></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><span> </span></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><span> </span></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}